<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard</title>
    <style>
         body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #89f7fe, #66a6ff);
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 70%;
            max-width: 900px;
        }

        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h3 {
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
        }

        li strong {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Welcome to Your Dashboard!</h2>
        <p>Welcome, <strong>User</strong>! This is your personalized dashboard where you can manage all your certifications, track their renewal deadlines, and update your profile. Use the menu on the left to navigate through various sections of the platform.</p>
        
        <h3>What Can You Do Here?</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Add Certifications:</strong> Add any professional certifications you have earned to your profile. You can easily upload certificates and track their details.</li>
            <li><strong>View Certifications:</strong> See a detailed list of all your certifications, including their issuance date and expiration dates.</li>
            <li><strong>Monitor Renewal Deadlines:</strong> Stay on top of certification renewal deadlines so you never miss a renewal date. You'll receive reminders in advance.</li>
            <li><strong>Update Your Profile:</strong> Keep your contact and personal information up to date. Ensure your profile reflects your current details.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
